// |  SHIFT   |  Z  |  X  |  C  |  V  |  B  |  N  |  M  |  / |  SHIFT  |    UP  |  1  |  2  |  3  |
// |  CTL | WIN |  ALT  |    SPACE     |       SPACE      | fn |    LEFT |  DOWN |RIGHT|  0  |  .  |
// -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
			bindings = <
    &kp ESC  &kp Q  &kp W  &kp E  &kp R  &kp T  &kp Y  &kp U  &kp I  &kp O  &kp P  &kp BSPC       &kp KP_N7    &kp KP_N8    &kp KP_N9
